title: Batman - Li'l Gotham 1-14 (2012-2013) (Digital) (Ongoing)
description:
English | CBR | 14 Issues

Batman: Li'l Gotham #1-14
Publisher:  DC Comics
Publication Date:  October 31, 2012 - July 7, 2013

Writer:  Dustin Nguyen and Derek Fridolfs
Art and Cover:  Dustin Nguyen
Letterer:  Saida Temofonte

Batman: Li'l Gotham is an ongoing bimonthly digital first comic.

Batman, Robin, and all your favorite Gothamites romp through the year in a very special series! This festive series is the brainchild of artist/writer Dustin Nguyen and co-writer Derek Fridolfs, and showcases Dustin's stunning water-color art to illustrate a story set against a holiday each month.

Thanks goes to Zone, TheHand, K6, Son of Ultron, and DCP for this release.
